item.title: Martians VS Robots
item.description: The brave Autobots entered into a deadly battle with the Decepticons. Choose one of 3 characters of this exciting game and try to win in all fights. Thanks to your help, the brave defenders of the Earth will definitely defeat their eternal enemies and save our planet from complete destruction.
